---
// WhoThisIsFor.astro
---

<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold uppercase text-brand-700 mb-8">
      Who This Is For
    </h2>
    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">
      This work is for leaders who own the outcome
    </h3>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      You're responsible for results across hiring, sales, and execution.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6">
      Not activity. Not intent. Outcomes.
    </p>
    <ul class="text-left inline-block text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
      <li>• CEOs and founders accountable for growth</li>
      <li>• Sales leaders responsible for revenue</li>
      <li>• Executives fixing hiring or execution gaps</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-base italic text-brand-500">
      If you're not accountable for results, this probably isn't for you.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>